<h3>Thursday, 2/13 from 5:30 PM to 8 PM</h3>
<h2>Gnocchi Cooking Class</h2>
<p><img align="none" style="float: right" alt="" src="" /></p>
<p>In this cooking class, Michela Tartaglia will coach you as YOU make gnocchi with quattro formaggi (Four Cheese Sauce: Parmigiano Reggiano, Fontina, Gorgonzola and Pecorino) sauce from scratch! At the end of the cooking class, we will enjoy our gnocchi in the spectacular atmosphere of Pasta Casalinga.</p>
<p>Appetizer and a glass of wine per person included. Additional wine/beer can be purchased.</p>
